channel.description: I don't know why but suddenly my computer can't play .midi files. Runescape music is .midi so i can't hear that either. Any1 know why this happened?

item.title: .midi?
item.dc:creator: @Etnies Etnies
item.description:
@Etnies wrote:

IDK, I use WMP and midis work just fine on mine, i mean MIDI is unsupported for most players. check your speakers.

Why the fuck do you even listen to MIDI files in the first place – they suck like crap and are bad for your ears. TRY MP3 files which play at 128+ kbps

i dont like runescape music, listen to slipknot instead
